00:21:58,576 --> 00:22:25,610
Councilor Scarpelli. If we can, I know that the director is leaving at seven. I know that we've had constituents that are here and on Zoom that wanted some answers directly to ask the director. I think that before we run out of time, I think we should let our residents an opportunity to ask some pretty important questions. And I'll hold my questions until after. I'd rather have the constituents, our residents have asked some questions first.

