00:22:51,850 --> 00:23:15,121
So the appeals clerk put together charts about, we've had folks, we've had two issues that we have discovered, actually three total. So when we first started doing enforcement, we noticed quite a few display decals on cars that were totally blank. And we didn't understand what was going on with that.

64
00:23:15,290 --> 00:23:26,073
